<pb facs="wfc.css00042.001" />

<div1 type="letter">


<opener>
<note type="letterhead">Howell Cobb. C.D.M. Cobb. Purcell House, Cobb Brothers, Prop's</note>


<dateline>
<address><addrLine>Wilmington, N.C.</addrLine></address>
<date>Oct 5th 1878</date>
</dateline>


<salute>My Dear Boy Michael</salute>
</opener>

<p>I know you are anxious to hear from me. I would have wrote you before but have been so <choice><sic>undicided</sic><corr>undecided</corr></choice> to know what I am going to do my self. theYellow Fever is so bad I may yet come back to Baltimore and if I do then I will arrange to send you away. if not I will write you in a few days what to do.</p>

<p>I hope you are all O.K. Write me to. Charleston. S. C. on receipt of this. Give my kind

<pb facs="wfc.css00042.002" />

regards to Your Father Mother &amp; the family</p>

<closer>
<salute>And <choice><sic>beleive</sic><corr>believe</corr></choice> me your friend</salute>

<signed>W. F. Cody</signed>
</closer>
</div1>


</body>

